pxchat.util
Class Config

java.lang.Object
  pxchat.util.Config

public final class Config
extends java.lang.Object

This static class contains the client configuration. It provides a mapping of keys to values and a list of connection profiles. The configuration file can be loaded by calling init(String) with a proper file name. By calling save(), the current configuration state is saved to the file this class was initialized with.
